dHYpicuhuctSgZqeTvDS/assets/static/optimized/rev-685694a/launchspace.net/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/47ebc7f919c77545dc90164e118a72a7.Affiliate-marketing.jpg 320w" nitro-lazy-src="https://cdn-blajl.nitrocdn.com/fVHWLpOdnAIhdHYpicuhuctSgZqeTvDS/assets/static/optimized/rev-685694a/launchspace.net/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/74f2343d2c9b4c4d0cb36c295c3e9e8a.Affiliate-marketing.jpg#038;ssl=1" class="wp-image-4873 nitro-lazy" nitro-lazy-empty="" id="NDczOjIwOTM=-1"  src="data:image/svg+xml;nitro-empty-id=NDczOjIwOTM=-1;base64,PHN2ZyB2aWV3Qm94PSIwIDAgNjk1IDI0NSIgd2lkdGg9IjY5NSIgaGVpZ2h0PSIyNDUiIHhtbG5zPSJodHRwOi8vd3d3LnczLm9yZy8yMDAwL3N2ZyI+PC9zdmc+"><noscript><img data-attachment-id="4873" data-permalink="https://launchspace.net/content-marketing/how-to-make-money-blogging/attachment/affiliate-marketing/" data-orig-file="https://i2.wp.com/launchspace.net/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/Affiliate-marketing.jpg?fit=695%2C245&amp;ssl=1" data-orig-size="695,245" data-comments-opened="0" data-image-meta="{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}" data-image-title="Affiliate-marketing" data-image-description="" data-image-caption="" data-medium-file="https://i2.wp.com/launchspace.net/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/Affiliate-marketing.jpg?fit=300%2C106&amp;ssl=1" data-large-file="https://i2.wp.com/launchspace.net/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/Affiliate-marketing.jpg?fit=695%2C245&amp;ssl=1" loading="lazy" width="695" height="245" src="https://i2.wp.com/launchspace.net/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/Affiliate-marketing.jpg?resize=695%2C245&#038;ssl=1" alt="" class="wp-image-4873" srcset="https://i2.wp.com/launchspace.net/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/Affiliate-marketing.jpg?w=695&amp;ssl=1 695w, https://i2.wp.com/launchspace.net/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/Affiliate-marketing.jpg?resize=300%2C106&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i2.wp.com/launchspace.net/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/Affiliate-marketing.jpg?resize=580%2C204&amp;ssl=1 580w, https://i2.wp.com/launchspace.net/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/Affiliate-marketing.jpg?resize=320%2C113&amp;ssl=1 320w" sizes="(max-width: 695px) 100vw, 695px" data-recalc-dims="1" /></noscript></figure> <p class="nitro-offscreen">You can see she gets around 1,000+ visitors a month who click through to Agoda. Yet her affiliate income from Agoda is around $100-$150 a month.</p> <p class="nitro-offscreen">That’s a terrible rate of return, and certainly not enough to live on.</p> <p class="nitro-offscreen">To make a decent commission from affiliate marketing, you need to find products with a high conversion rate and a high payout rate. In an ideal world, you’ll find products with both.</p> <p class="nitro-offscreen">I just shared how to earn an income as an affiliate marketer passively through your blog.</p> <p class="nitro-offscreen">You can improve your conversion rate by warming up the lead before making a recommendation. The most successful affiliate marketers I know use multiple marketing channels to make their recommendations. For example, they run promotions through an email list or on a webinar. Both of these channels have higher conversion rates than cold traffic from a blog. Then, they might run retargeting ads to people who didn’t purchase the offer.</p> <h3 class="nitro-offscreen">Sell Products Or Courses</h3> <p class="nitro-offscreen">When you look at the income stream of pro bloggers, you’ll notice many of them earn a large portion of their income from selling courses. Not convinced. Here’s a couple of examples:</p> <ul class="nitro-offscreen"><li>Matt Diggity from Diggity Marketing</li><li>Brian Dean from Backlinko</li><li>Pat Flynn from Smart Passive Income</li><li>Glen Alsopp from Detailed</li><li>Michelle Schroeder from Making Sense of Cents</li></ul> <p class="nitro-offscreen">All of those bloggers sell expensive courses. These courses typically cost from a couple of hundred dollars to $1,000+.</p> <p class="nitro-offscreen">With a large audience, you can generate a lot of money selling courses. Even with a small audience, you don’t need to convert many leads to earn a nice income from a thousand-dollar course.</p> <p class="nitro-offscreen">It’s part of the reason I want to launch an <a href="https://launchspace.net/content-marketing/seo-certification/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">SEO certification course</a>.</p> <p class="nitro-offscreen">Information products and courses provide you with a great way to make money fast from your blog. With the right marketing strategy in place, you can get a 20%+ conversion rate from online webinars. I discuss <a href="https://blog.hubspot.com/sales/sell-online-course-webinar" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">how to sell online courses on a webinar</a> in an article on Hubspot.</p> <p class="nitro-offscreen">You can also sell information products or physical products.</p> <p class="nitro-offscreen">For example, my wife received 140 orders for tours on her travel website during over a 30-day period. She made $10,000+ in gross sales, generating a profit margin of $2,000+. </p> <figure class="wp-block-image nitro-offscreen"><img data-attachment-id="4874" data-permalink="https://launchspace.net/content-marketing/how-to-make-money-blogging/attachment/how-to-make-money-blogging-selling-a-service/" data-orig-file="https://i1.wp.com/launchspace.net/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/How-to-make-money-blogging-selling-a-service.jpg?fit=791%2C513&ssl=1" data-orig-size="791,513" data-comments-opened="0" data-image-meta="{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}" data-image-title="How-to-make-money-blogging-selling-a-service" data-image-description="" data-image-caption="" data-medium-file="https://i1.wp.com/launchspace.net/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/How-to-make-money-blogging-selling-a-service.jpg?fit=300%2C195&ssl=1" data-large-file="https://i1.wp.com/launchspace.net/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/How-to-make-money-blogging-selling-a-service.jpg?fit=720%2C467&ssl=1" width="720" height="467" alt="" data-recalc-dims="1" data-lazy-srcset="https://cdn-blajl.nitrocdn.com/fVHWLpOdnAIhdHYpicuhuctSgZqeTvDS/assets/static/optimized/rev-685694a/launchspace.net/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/4e3a554d6fa0dfbeec52eda22fd803a6.How-to-make-money-blogging-selling-a-service.jpg 791w, https://cdn-blajl.nitrocdn.com/fVHWLpOdnAIhdHYpicuhuctSgZqeTvDS/assets/static/optimized/rev-685694a/launchspace.net/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/351c3a7bed25ca91bb0d10b459b97476.How-to-make-money-blogging-selling-a-service.jpg 300w, https://cdn-blajl.nitrocdn.com/fVHWLpOdnAIhdHYpicuhuctSgZqeTvDS/assets/static/optimized/rev-685694a/launchspace.net/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/f7da9dcabfe3cd40eb76648ae8b307d6.How-to-make-money-blogging-selling-a-service.jpg 768w, https://cdn-blajl.nitrocdn.com/fVHWLpOdnAIhdHYpicuhuctSgZqeTvDS/assets/static/optimized/rev-685694a/launchspace.net/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/66b78522c485e61e7c07af3bd21bf5d3.How-to-make-money-blogging-selling-a-service.jpg 720w, https://cdn-blajl.nitrocdn.com/fVHWLpOdnAIhdHYpicuhuctSgZqeTvDS/assets/static/optimized/rev-685694a/launchspace.net/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/f3132cac1314c6e84e02cba92bd25f67.How-to-make-money-blogging-selling-a-service.jpg 580w, https://cdn-blajl.nitrocdn.com/fVHWLpOdnAIhdHYpicuhuctSgZqeTvDS/assets/static/optimized/rev-685694a/launchspace.net/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/471d9bdff990aef